Question

Where are both species of numbats most frequently spotted in Australia?

Australia <- get_stamenmap(bbox = c(left = 110.338, bottom = -38.961, right = 162.457, top = -11.912), maptype = 'terrain', zoom = 5)
##  Map tiles by Stamen Design, under CC BY 3.0. Data by OpenStreetMap, under ODbL.
ggmap(Australia) + 
  geom_point(data = numbats, aes(x = decimalLongitude, y = decimalLatitude, color = scientificName), alpha = 0.75, size = 2) +
  theme_map() +
  theme(legend.position = 'right') +
  labs(title = 'Location of numbat sightings in Australia by species')
## Warning: Removed 83 rows containing missing values (`geom_point()`).
